narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would not recommend this class for another student because it was not the class as advertised on OCI. It did not follow the syllabus and every week was the same lesson. I was bored and unengaged. This class was not useful for me.
I would recommend this class based on the reading list or if you like Professor Anderson's teaching style.
Take it--both for the excellent reading list and the prof.
No. I learned little and it was very frustrating.
